cGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012742, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay paak o paakeeza hast aap par salaam ho. Salaam ho aap par ay woh zaat jis ko Khuda ne buland sharaf se makhsoos kiya. Aap par salaam ho ay woh hasti jiski peshaani se sayyadul ambiya ka noor roshan huwa, jiske zariye se zameen o aasmaan roshan huwe.", "Urdu": "اے پاک و پاکیزہ ہستی آپ پر سلام ہو، سلام ہو آپ پر اے وہ ذات جس کو خدا نے بلند شرف سے مخصوص کیا، آپ پر سلام ہو اے وہ ہستی جس کی پیشانئ سے سید الانبیاء کا نور روشن ہوا جس کے ذریعہ سے زمین و آسمان روشن ہو گئے۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE AYYATOHAT TAAHERATUL MOTAHHARATO ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE YAA MAN KHASSAHAL LAAHO BE-A-A’LASH SHARAFE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE YAA MAN SATA-A’ MIN JABEENEHAA NOORO SAYYEDIL AMBEYAAA-E FA-AZAA-AT BEHIL ARZO WAS SAMAAA-O.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ اَیَّتُہَا الطَّاہِرَۃُ الْمُطَہَّرَۃُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا مَنْ خَصَّہَا اللهُ بِاَعْلَی الشَّرَفِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا مَنْ سَطَعَ مِنْ جَبِیْنِہَا نُوْرُ سَیِّدِ الْاَنْبِیَآئِ فَاَضَائَتْ بِہِ الْاَرْضُ وَالسَّمَآئُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012743, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par salaam ho ay woh bibi jiske liye malaayeka naazil huwe aur jinke liye Jannat ke hijaab (pardeh) utha diye gaye. Aap par salaam ho ay woh mohtarma bibi jiski khidmat ke liye Hoor’ain Jannat se naazil huwi aur jis ko sharaab’e Jannat se seraab kiya gaya aur Khairul Ambiya ki wilaadat ki bashaarat di gayi.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے وہ بی بی جس کے لئے ملائکہ نازل ہوئے اور جن کے لئے جنت کے حجاب اٹھا دیے گئے، آپ پر سلام ہو اے وہ محترم بی بی جس کی خدمت کے لئے حورعین جنت سے نازل ہوئیں اور جس کو شراب جنت سے سیراب کیا گیا اور خیر الانبیاء کی ولادت کی بشارت دی گئی۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE YAA MAN NAZALAT LE-AJLEHAL MALAAA-EKATO WA ZOREBAT LAHAA HOJOBUL JANNATE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE YAA MAN NAZALAT LE-KHIDMATEHAL HOORUL E’ENO WA SAQAYNAHAA MIN SHARAABIL JANNATE WA BASH-SHARTAHAA BEWELAADATE KHAYRIL AMBEYAAA-E.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا مَنْ نَزَلَتْ لِاَجْلِہَا الْمَلَآئِكَۃُ وَضُرِبَتْ لَہَا حُجُبُ الْجَنَّۃِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا مَنْ نَزَلَتْ لِخِدْمَتِہَا الْحُوْرُ الْعِی